name: Censor this!
description:
Society constantly reminds women of how we need to act and what we need to look like to BE a woman. This art piece amplifies the message that we WILL NOT be censored and we are done with society’s obsession with sexualizing our bodies!

We are strong, amazing, badass women who deserve respect no matter what we look like. Because being a woman doesn’t mean you have to fit in a box that society has constructed!
